'''硫酸铝钠'''是一种无机化合物，化学式为NaAl(SO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>·12H<sub>2</sub>O，有时候写作Na<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub>·Al<sub>2</sub>(SO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>·24H<sub>2</sub>O)，又称钠明矾。它是白色固体，可用于食物（[[E编码|E521]]）的[[酸度调节剂|酸度调节剂]]，主要用于[[发粉|发粉]]的制造。

==概况==
硫酸铝钠由[[硫酸铝|硫酸铝]]和[[硫酸钠|硫酸钠]]化合得到，其年产量有3000吨（2003年）。在美国，它经常与[[碳酸氢钠|碳酸氢钠]]、[[磷酸氢钙|磷酸氢钙]]一起使用，在家用设备中用作焙烤粉。<ref name=Ullmann>Otto Helmboldt, L. Keith Hudson, Chanakya Misra, Karl Wefers, Wolfgang Heck, Hans Stark, Max Danner, Norbert Rösch "Aluminum Compounds, Inorganic" in Ullmann's Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry 2007, Wiley-VCH, Weinheim.{{DOI|10.1002/14356007.a01_527.pub2}}</ref>

经典的立方明矾结构以十二水合物形式存在，[[矿物学|矿物学]]中称其为钠明矾。<ref>{{citation | first = Ernst A.J. | last = Burke | title = Tidying up mineral names: an IMA-CNMNC scheme for suffixes, hyphens and diacritical marks | url = http://pubsites.uws.edu.au/ima-cnmnc/tidyingupnames.pdf | journal = Mineralogical Record | volume = 39 | issue = 2 | year = 2008 | pages = 131–35 | access-date = 2017-02-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120326093254/http://pubsites.uws.edu.au/ima-cnmnc/tidyingupnames.pdf | archive-date = 2012-03-26 | dead-url = yes }}.</ref><ref>{{WebMineral | name = Alum-(Na) | url = http://webmineral.com/data/Alum-%28Na%29.shtml | accessdate = 2009-11-28}}.{{Mindat | name = Alum-(Na) | id = 3703 | accessdate = 2009-11-28}}.</ref>它也以另外两种罕见矿物的形式出现——水钠铝矾（mendozite）（十一水合物）<ref>{{WebMineral | name = Mendozite | url = http://webmineral.com/data/Mendozite.shtml | accessdate = 2009-11-28}}.{{Mindat | name = Mendozite | id = 2643 | accessdate = 2009-11-28}}.</ref>和斜钠明矾（tamarugite）（六水合物）。<ref>{{WebMineral | name = Tamarugite | url = http://www.webmineral.com/data/Tamarugite.shtml | accessdate = 2009-11-28}}.{{Mindat | name = Tamarugite | id = 3878 | accessdate = 2009-11-28}}.</ref>

它也是用于在组织病理学中染色[[细胞核|细胞核]]的[[苏木精|苏木精]]溶液的常用[[媒染剂|媒染剂]]。

